dialog.body: Hello, thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Edward Rivera. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Samantha. Can you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is eight five six two one and my date of birth is zero four slash eighteen slash one nine eight seven.
Thank you, Samantha. I also need the make and model of your vehicle along with the VIN number. Could you please provide those details?
Of course. The vehicle is a two zero one eight Honda Civic and the VIN number is J A H N zero three four five six seven eight nine zero one two three.
Great, thank you for the information, Samantha. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that was all. Thank you for your help, Edward.
You're welcome, Samantha. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a wonderful day!
Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Goodbye.
